Body: Description: Users are granted read only access in the NEA console, however when trying to open the console the user is presented a message "error code 5. Access denied"
What We've Learned Updated: User has been given permission to access the NEA console, however when trying to start the console the error "error code 5. Access denied" is thrown.
Next Steps Updated: Awaiting customer DB team to create missing permission groups detailed in documentation.

What We've Learned Updated: User has been given permission to access the NEA console, however when trying to start the console the error "error code 5. Access denied" is thrown.
We verified that the user does not have proper permissions applied at the SQL server and needs to be updated
Next Steps Updated: Awaiting customer DB team to create missing permission groups detailed in documentation and customer to test again.
